data.description: Ackerman Meadows enjoys one of the best locations in greater San Antonio, with outstanding access to the major corridors of IH-10, IH-35, and Loop 410 and Loop 1604 and proximity to Randolph Air Force Base and Fort Sam Houston. Located in the highly desirable Northeast Side, Ackerman Meadows provides an ideal neighborhood for military families. Major retailers, entertainment, parks and recreation, grocery stores and other conveniences, along with some of the best Tex-Mex and barbecue restaurants around, are all within a few miles. San Antonio's iconic RiverWalk is less than 15 miles away, along with the fabulous Majestic Theatre, the Alamodome, home of basketball's Spurs, and, of course, the Alamo. Children are eligible to attend nearby Judson Independent School District's Masters Elementary, Metzger Middle, and Wagner High schools.
